	<div class="entry" id="entry1">
    	<h1 class="ex-interviews"><a href="/interviews/adrian-cole-jclouds">What’s Next for jclouds?</a></h1>
    	
        	<p class="image"><a href="/interviews/adrian-cole-jclouds"><img src="/resource/interviews/adrian-cole-jclouds/en/smallimage/cole.JPG" alt="" /></a></p>
        
        <p>Adrian Cole discusses his jclouds project, which is an open source library that helps Java developers get started in the cloud using their Java development skills. Cole also discusses jclouds’ future.</p>
        <ul class="info link-col" style="margin-left:0px;">
            <li>
							
				<a href="/operations" name="operations" id="5,827" onclick="try {CategoryPopup.showPopup(this);} catch(e) {}; return false;">Operations</a>,				
				
							
				<a href="/java" name="java" id="1" onclick="try {CategoryPopup.showPopup(this);} catch(e) {}; return false;">Java</a>,				
				
			
			</li>
	        <li class="author">	        	
	        	
					
				
				<strong><a
	
	href="/author/Adrian-Cole"

 class="editorlink">
Adrian Cole</a>
